ay to play scenario,\\\" McMorris wrote.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Mark McMorris (@markmcmorris)    In his attempt to land the jump posted above, McMorris kneed himself in the face, causing several injuries.\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McMorris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark McMorris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McMorris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McMorris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needed surgery at Vancouver General Hospital.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_General_Hospital\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver General Hospital\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_General_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_General_Hospital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I thought was a black eye turned out to be a more severe injury,\\\" McMorris said.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On Monday, I underwent surgery at VGH to have my orbital bone and nose repaired.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_General_Hospital\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"VGH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_General_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_General_Hospital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Brown and his team did a stellar job, and I am now officially on the mend.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you all for the kind messages and healing vibes!\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It mea